episodes.natural_language:
Case Nyiana-Davis-MVA-6-14-2025 concerns Nyiana Davis, who was involved in a motor vehicle accident on June 14, 2025 at the corner of Lexington Road and Payne Street in Louisville, Kentucky, while riding in a Lyft. The incident was reported to the Louisville Metro Police Department under Report Number 25067954, and the Lyft driver was Justice Akubia.

Nyiana Davis was born on January 15, 2003. Her Social Security number is 228-95-9489. She resides at 1836 Eastern Parkway, Apt B1, Louisville, KY 40204, and her phone number is 502-851-1119.

At the time of the crash, she was sitting in the back seat behind the driver; the Lyft driver ran a red light and t-boned another vehicle.

She went to UofL Hospital downtown for evaluation and care. Injuries noted include right-sided pain and a right knee injury.

Nyiana Davis has Anthem health insurance.
episodes.author: Justin Chumbley
